{"tid":1534872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人既最後手段係咩？","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T18:09:24.000Z","uid":201178,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2d15fe4f553731859c4d06870511fe8b8c9a260d","tid":1534872,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:53:52.000Z","msg":"岩岩見有個post講<br />\n「警察係咪要迫香港人行到最後一步？」<br />\n咁其實最後一步又係咩<br />\n721就話黑社會姐，831已經警察係打人，<br />\n已經係人道問題，差到無得再差，咁既時候香港人連罷工罷課都做唔到，<br />\n咁到底香港人最後一步係咩？<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係失敗主義，只係想討論下到底香港人底線到邊"},{"pid":"5b3b3f620bb6590bc648785cbac38fbf521f56fb","tid":1534872,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:53:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb38889f93f2fd4ed29c75b27fde279de2ac2891","tid":1534872,"uid":102700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:54:27.000Z","msg":"香港人最後一步=返屋企訓覺"},{"pid":"8a274fa8c4aab749592982dcc3e6f2ba7ea8c4e7","tid":1534872,"uid":17502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1